                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If fs.&amp;lt;filesyste&amp;gt;.impl.disable.cache  (eg fs.hdfs.impl.disable.cache) is set to true, then table rename fails.&lt;/p&gt;


